name: 泰克
introduction: Born in Malaysia, Teck grew up in the mid-west speaking Chinese and taught herself English by listening to rap music. She is an Asian-American director and actress known for her role as Elyse in Don't Sweat the Small Stuff: The Kristine Carson Story (2021), performing her own stunts in RideShare (2021) and starring in Thomas Rhett's music video Slow Down Summer (2021).Teck has directed a handful of music videos, mini-documentaries, and commercials in over 15 states and 3 countries preparing her way into the narrative feature-length world.
